          <div>
            <h4><a href="https://northwestbronx.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Northwest Bronx Community &amp; Clergy Coalition</a></h4>
            <p>One of the oldest community organizing coalitions in the city.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="org">
          <div>
            <h4><a href="https://mothersonthemove.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mothers on the Move</a></h4>
